{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775868911638,"sessionID":"ses_285f9278affers42EQBy8xMnAS","part":{"id":"prt_d7a091fb0001nkg4Zb72eWveIx","messageID":"msg_d7a075ab7001UlTOGGYYfH4QIO","sessionID":"ses_285f9278affers42EQBy8xMnAS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-117a97219e524aaca05acc246868da75","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md","content":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Infrastructure (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` with project configuration\n  - Project name: `kubectl-agentcube`\n  - Version: `0.1.0`\n  - Dependencies: `typer[all]>=0.9.0`, `pydantic>=2.0.0`, `pyyaml>=6.0`, `rich>=13.0.0`\n  - Dev dependencies: `pytest>=7.4.0`, `pytest-mock>=3.11.0`\n  - Console script: `kubectl-agentcube = agentcube.cli.main:app`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`\n  - Verification: `pip install -e cmd/cli && kubectl-agentcube --help`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py` with package exports\n  - Define `__version__ = \"0.1.0\"`\n  - Export `app` from `agentcube.cli.main`\n  - Export `PackRuntime`, `MetadataOptions` from `agentcube.runtime`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube import __version__, app; print(__version__)\"`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py` as subpackage marker\n  - Empty file or docstring for CLI subpackage\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"import agentcube.cli\"`\n\n### Phase 2: Models Layer (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py` as package marker\n  - Export `MetadataOptions` from `pack_models`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.models import MetadataOptions\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py` with `MetadataOptions` dataclass\n  - Fields: `agent_name`, `language='python'`, `entrypoint`, `port=8080`, `build_mode='local'`, `requirements_file`, `description`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port=8080`, `registry_url`, `registry_username`, `registry_password`, `agent_endpoint`\n  - Method: `from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> MetadataOptions`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.models import MetadataOptions; m = MetadataOptions(); print(m.language)\"`\n\n### Phase 3: Services Layer (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` with package docstring\n  - Export `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` from `metadata_service`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.services import AgentMetadata\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` with `AgentMetadata` model\n  - Pydantic `BaseModel` with fields: `agent_name`, `description`, `language='python'`, `entrypoint`, `port=8080`, `build_mode='local'`, `region`, `version`, `image`, `auth`, `requirements_file='requirements.txt'`, `registry_url`, `registry_username`, `registry_password`, `agent_endpoint`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port`, `agent_id`, `session_id`, `k8s_deployment`\n  - Validators: `validate_language` (python/java), `validate_build_mode` (local/cloud), `validate_port` (1-65535)\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.services import AgentMetadata; m = AgentMetadata(agent_name='test', entrypoint='python main.py'); print(m.language)\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` with `MetadataService` class\n  - Constructor: `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n  - Method: `load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata` — try `agent_metadata.yaml`, `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml` in order\n  - Method: `save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Path` — save to `agent_metadata.yaml`\n  - YAML dump settings: `default_flow_style=False`, `indent=2`, `sort_keys=False`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.services import MetadataService; print(MetadataService)\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` with `DockerService` class\n  - Constructor: `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n  - Method: `check_docker_available(self) -> bool` — check Docker CLI availability\n  - Method: `build_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str` — placeholder for AR-021\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.services import DockerService; print(DockerService)\"`\n\n### Phase 4: PackRuntime Core Logic (ST-4)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` with exports\n  - Export `PackRuntime` from `pack_runtime`\n  - Export `MetadataOptions` from `agentcube.models`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime import PackRuntime, MetadataOptions\"`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` with `PackRuntime.__init__`\n  - Constructor: `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n  - Initialize: `self._metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose)`\n  - Initialize: `self._docker_service = DockerService(verbose)`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime import PackRuntime; r = PackRuntime(); print(r.verbose)\"`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3**: Implement `PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path)`\n  - Check `workspace_path.exists()` — raise `ValueError` if not\n  - Check `workspace_path.is_dir()` — raise `ValueError` if not\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_validate_workspace_structure -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.4**: Implement `PackRuntime._load_or_create_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, options: Dict) -> AgentMetadata`\n  - Try loading from `agent_metadata.yaml`, `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml` (first match wins)\n  - If none exist: create new with defaults from options + workspace name\n  - Infer entrypoint if not provided: Python → `main.py` or first `.py` file; Java → `java -jar app.jar`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_load_or_create_metadata -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.5**: Implement `PackRuntime._apply_option_overrides(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict) -> AgentMetadata`\n  - Override `agent_name` if `options['agent_name']` provided\n  - Override `language` if `options['language']` provided\n  - Override `entrypoint` if `options['entrypoint']` provided\n  - Override `port` if `options['port']` provided\n  - Override `build_mode` if `options['build_mode']` provided\n  - Override `description` if `options['description']` provided\n  - Return updated metadata\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_apply_option_overrides -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.6**: Implement `PackRuntime._validate_language_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata)`\n  - Python: check for at least one `.py` file — raise `ValueError` if missing\n  - Java: check for `pom.xml` — raise `ValueError` if missing\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_validate_language_compatibility -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.7**: Implement `PackRuntime._process_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata)`\n  - Python: check `requirements.txt` exists (warning if missing, continue)\n  - Java: no additional processing (pom.xml handles dependencies)\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_process_dependencies -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.8**: Implement `PackRuntime._generate_dockerfile(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Optional[Path]`\n  - If `Dockerfile` exists: return path (no regeneration)\n  - If missing: generate based on `metadata.language`\n  - Python template: `FROM python:3.10-slim`, pip install, expose port\n  - Java template: multi-stage Maven build → JRE runtime\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_generate_dockerfile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.9**: Implement `PackRuntime._generate_python_dockerfile(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str`\n  - Template: `FROM python:3.10-slim`, `WORKDIR /app`, `COPY requirements.txt`, `RUN pip install`, `COPY .`, `EXPOSE {port}`, `CMD [{entrypoint}]`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_generate_python_dockerfile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.10**: Implement `PackRuntime._generate_java_dockerfile(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str`\n  - Template: Multi-stage with `maven:3.8-openjdk-17` build → `openjdk:17-slim` runtime\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_generate_java_dockerfile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.11**: Implement `PackRuntime._update_pack_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata, dockerfile_path: Optional[Path])`\n  - Set `metadata.image = {\"dockerfile_path\": str(dockerfile_path)}` if dockerfile exists\n  - Save metadata via `self._metadata_service.save_metadata()`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_update_pack_metadata -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.12**: Implement `PackRuntime.pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n  - Execute full workflow: validate → load metadata → apply overrides → validate language → process deps → generate dockerfile → update metadata\n  - Return dict: `{\"agent_name\", \"workspace_path\", \"metadata_path\", \"dockerfile_path\", \"status\"}`\n  - Catch exceptions: set `status=\"error\"` and raise\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_pack_full_workflow -v`\n\n### Phase 5: CLI Command Layer (ST-5)\n\n- [ ] **T5.1**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` with Typer app setup\n  - Create `app = typer.Typer(help=\"AgentCube CLI for agent lifecycle management\")`\n  - Create `console = Console()` from Rich\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `kubectl-agentcube --help`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2**: Implement `_handle_error(e: Exception, command_name: str, verbose: bool)` helper\n  - Print `[red]Error {command_name}: {e}[/red]`\n  - Print traceback if `verbose=True`\n  - Exit with `typer.Exit(1)`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_cli.py::test_handle_error -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.3**: Implement `pack()` command with all CLI options\n  - Options: `--workspace/-f` (default \".\"), `--agent-name`, `--language`, `--entrypoint`, `--port`, `--build-mode`, `--description`, `--output`, `--verbose`\n  - Resolve `workspace_path = Path(workspace).resolve()`\n  - Build `options` dict from CLI arguments\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `kubectl-agentcube pack --help`\n\n- [ ] **T5.4**: Implement `pack()` command execution with progress spinner\n  - Use `rich.progress.Progress` with `SpinnerColumn`, `TextColumn`\n  - Create `PackRuntime(verbose)` and call `runtime.pack(workspace_path, **options)`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_cli.py::test_pack_command_execution -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.5**: Implement `pack()` command success output formatting\n  - Print: `[green]Success![/green] Agent [bold]{agent_name}[/bold] packed`\n  - Print: `Workspace: {path}`, `Metadata: {path}`, `Dockerfile: {path}`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_cli.py::test_pack_success_output -v`\n\n- [ ] **T5.6**: Implement `pack()` command error handling with `_handle_error`\n  - Wrap `PackRuntime.pack()` in try-except\n  - Call `_handle_error(e, \"pack\", verbose)` on exception\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest tests/test_pack_cli.py::test_pack_error_handling -v`\n\n### Phase 6: Example Workspaces (ST-6)\n\n- [ ] **T6.1**: Create `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/main.py` example agent\n  - Simple Python agent: print \"Hello from AgentCube!\"\n  - File: `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/main.py`\n  - Verification: `python cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/main.py`\n\n- [ ] **T6.2**: Create `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/requirements.txt`\n  - Empty or minimal dependencies\n  - File: `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/requirements.txt`\n  - Verification: `cat cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/requirements.txt`\n\n- [ ] **T6.3**: Create `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/main.py` example agent\n  - Simple math operations agent\n  - File: `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/main.py`\n  - Verification: `python cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/main.py`\n\n- [ ] **T6.4**: Create `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/requirements.txt`\n  - Minimal dependencies\n  - File: `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/requirements.txt`\n  - Verification: `cat cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/requirements.txt`\n\n### Phase 7: Unit Tests (ST-7)\n\n- [ ] **T7.1**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py` as test package marker\n  - Empty file or docstring\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"import tests\"`\n\n- [ ] **T7.2**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with workspace validation tests\n  - `test_validate_workspace_structure_exists`: valid directory → pass\n  - `test_validate_workspace_structure_not_exists`: non-existent → ValueError\n  - `test_validate_workspace_structure_not_directory`: file path → ValueError\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_validate_workspace_structure -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.3**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with metadata loading tests\n  - `test_load_metadata_from_agent_metadata_yaml`: load primary file\n  - `test_load_metadata_fallback_agent_yaml`: fallback to agent.yaml\n  - `test_load_metadata_fallback_metadata_yaml`: fallback to metadata.yaml\n  - `test_create_metadata_no_files`: create new with defaults\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_load -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.4**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with option override tests\n  - `test_apply_override_agent_name`: override agent_name\n  - `test_apply_override_language`: override language\n  - `test_apply_override_port`: override port\n  - `test_apply_override_build_mode`: override build_mode\n  - `test_apply_override_no_changes`: no overrides → unchanged\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_apply_override -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.5**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with language compatibility tests\n  - `test_validate_python_has_py_files`: Python with .py files → pass\n  - `test_validate_python_no_py_files`: Python without .py → ValueError\n  - `test_validate_java_has_pom`: Java with pom.xml → pass\n  - `test_validate_java_no_pom`: Java without pom.xml → ValueError\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_validate_language -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.6**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with Dockerfile generation tests\n  - `test_generate_dockerfile_existing`: existing Dockerfile → return path, no regeneration\n  - `test_generate_dockerfile_python_new`: Python workspace → generate Python template\n  - `test_generate_dockerfile_java_new`: Java workspace → generate Java template\n  - `test_dockerfile_content_python`: verify Python Dockerfile content\n  - `test_dockerfile_content_java`: verify Java Dockerfile content\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_dockerfile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.7**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with full workflow tests\n  - `test_pack_full_workflow_python`: end-to-end Python pack\n  - `test_pack_full_workflow_java`: end-to-end Java pack\n  - `test_pack_result_fields`: verify result dict has all fields\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_pack_full -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.8**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py` with CLI command tests\n  - `test_pack_cli_help`: `--help` shows usage\n  - `test_pack_cli_valid_workspace`: valid pack execution\n  - `test_pack_cli_invalid_workspace`: error on invalid workspace\n  - `test_pack_cli_verbose_output`: verbose mode shows traceback\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.9**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py` with metadata model tests\n  - `test_agent_metadata_valid`: valid metadata creation\n  - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_language`: invalid language → ValidationError\n  - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode`: invalid build_mode → ValidationError\n  - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_port`: port out of range → ValidationError\n  - `test_metadata_service_load`: load from YAML file\n  - `test_metadata_service_save`: save to YAML file\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\n\n### Phase 8: Integration & Validation (ST-8)\n\n- [ ] **T8.1**: Verify pyproject.toml installation\n  - `pip install -e cmd/cli` succeeds\n  - `kubectl-agentcube --version` prints `0.1.0`\n  - `kubectl-agentcube --help` shows pack command\n  - File: `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`\n  - Verification: `pip install -e cmd/cli && kubectl-agentcube --version`\n\n- [ ] **T8.2**: Verify pack command on hello-agent example\n  - `kubectl-agentcube pack -f cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent` succeeds\n  - `agent_metadata.yaml` created in workspace\n  - `Dockerfile` created in workspace\n  - File: `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/`\n  - Verification: `kubectl-agentcube pack -f cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent && cat cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/agent_metadata.yaml`\n\n- [ ] **T8.3**: Verify pack command with CLI overrides\n  - `kubectl-agentcube pack -f cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent --agent-name custom-agent --port 9000` succeeds\n  - Metadata reflects overridden values\n  - File: `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/`\n  - Verification: `kubectl-agentcube pack -f cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent --agent-name custom-agent --port 9000 && grep \"custom-agent\" cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/agent_metadata.yaml`\n\n- [ ] **T8.4**: Verify pack command error handling\n  - `kubectl-agentcube pack -f /nonexistent/path` exits with code 1\n  - Error message displayed\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `kubectl-agentcube pack -f /nonexistent || echo \"Exit code: $?\"`\n\n- [ ] **T8.5**: Run all tests with coverage\n  - `pytest cmd/cli/tests -v` passes\n  - Coverage > 80% for `pack_runtime.py`, `metadata_service.py`, `main.py`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests -v --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3\n         ↓\n      T2.1 → T2.2\n         ↓\n      T3.1 → T3.2 → T3.3 → T3.4\n               ↓\n      T4.1 → T4.2 → T4.3 → T4.4 → T4.5 → T4.6 → T4.7 → T4.8 → T4.9 → T4.10 → T4.11 → T4.12\n               ↓\n      T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3 → T5.4 → T5.5 → T5.6\n               ↓\n      T6.1 → T6.2 → T6.3 → T6.4\n               ↓\n      T7.1 → T7.2 → T7.3 → T7.4 → T7.5 → T7.6 → T7.7 → T7.8 → T7.9\n               ↓\n      T8.1 → T8.2 → T8.3 → T8.4 → T8.5\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| Install package | `pip install -e cmd/cli` |\n| CLI version check | `kubectl-agentcube --version` |\n| CLI help check | `kubectl-agentcube --help` |\n| Pack command help | `kubectl-agentcube pack --help` |\n| Pack example workspace | `kubectl-agentcube pack -f cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent` |\n| Run all tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests -v` |\n| Run with coverage | `pytest cmd/cli/tests --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` |\n| Runtime tests only | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py -v` |\n| CLI tests only | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py -v` |\n| Metadata tests only | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py -v` |\n| Python import check | `python -c \"from agentcube import PackRuntime, MetadataOptions\"` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `kubectl-agentcube pack -f /path/to/workspace` validates workspace structure\n- [ ] Creates `agent_metadata.yaml` if missing, loads from fallback files if present\n- [ ] CLI options (`--agent-name`, `--language`, `--entrypoint`, `--port`, `--build-mode`, `--description`) override metadata values\n- [ ] Python workspace validation: requires at least one `.py` file\n- [ ] Java workspace validation: requires `pom.xml`\n- [ ] Generates Dockerfile if missing, preserves existing Dockerfile\n- [ ] Python Dockerfile template: `FROM python:3.10-slim`, pip install, expose port\n- [ ] Java Dockerfile template: Multi-stage Maven build → JRE runtime\n- [ ] Saves updated metadata to `{workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n- [ ] Rich progress spinner during pack operation\n- [ ] Success output: agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path, dockerfile_path\n- [ ] Error output: colored error message, traceback if --verbose, exit code 1\n- [ ] Port validation: 1-65535 range\n- [ ] Language validation: 'python' or 'java' only\n- [ ] Build mode validation: 'local' or 'cloud' only\n- [ ] `pyproject.toml` defines console script entry point\n- [ ] Unit tests cover workspace validation, metadata loading, Dockerfile generation\n- [ ] Integration tests cover full pack workflow\n- [ ] `pytest cmd/cli/tests -v` passes all tests\n- [ ] Coverage > 80% for core modules\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines Changed | Description |\n|------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n| `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` | Create | ~40 | Project config, dependencies, console scripts |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py` | Create | ~15 | Package exports, version |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | CLI subpackage marker |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` | Create | ~80 | Typer app, pack command, error handler |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Models subpackage exports |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | Create | ~30 | MetadataOptions dataclass |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Create | ~10 | Runtime subpackage exports |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | Create | ~150 | PackRuntime class with pack workflow |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Create | ~10 | Services subpackage exports |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Create | ~100 | AgentMetadata model, MetadataService |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Create | ~40 | DockerService (placeholder) |\n| `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/main.py` | Create | ~10 | Example Python agent |\n| `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/requirements.txt` | Create | ~2 | Empty requirements |\n| `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/main.py` | Create | ~20 | Example math agent |\n| `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/requirements.txt` | Create | ~2 | Minimal requirements |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Test package marker |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` | Create | ~200 | PackRuntime unit tests |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py` | Create | ~80 | CLI pack command tests |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py` | Create | ~100 | MetadataService tests |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n- **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n- **Metadata file resolution order**: `agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml`\n- **Entrypoint inference**: Python → `main.py` or first `.py` file; Java → `java -jar app.jar`\n- **Dockerfile generation**: Preserve existing Dockerfile, generate only if missing\n- **YAML dump settings**: `default_flow_style=False`, `indent=2`, `sort_keys=False`, `exclude_none=True`\n- **Language templates**: Python (`python:3.10-slim`), Java (multi-stage Maven build)\n- **Dependencies**: `typer[all]>=0.9.0`, `pydantic>=2.0.0`, `pyyaml>=6.0`, `rich>=13.0.0`\n- **Console script**: `kubectl-agentcube = agentcube.cli.main:app`\n- **Integration points**:\n  - `MetadataService` — metadata load/save operations\n  - `DockerService` — placeholder for AR-021 build integration\n- **Error handling**: `typer.Exit(1)` on exception, traceback with `--verbose`\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Project Infrastructure | T1.1, T1.2, T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Models Layer | T2.1, T2.2 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Services Layer | T3.1, T3.2, T3.3, T3.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: PackRuntime Core Logic | T4.1-T4.12 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: CLI Command Layer | T5.1, T5.2, T5.3, T5.4, T5.5, T5.6 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Example Workspaces | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Unit Tests | T7.1-T7.9 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Integration & Validation | T8.1-T8.5 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/45 tasks)**"},"ou